## Wzorzec Observer — EventDispatcher

```php
interface EventInterface {
    public function getName(): string;
    public function getPayload(): array;
}

class EventDispatcher {
    private array $listeners = [];

    public function subscribe(string $event, callable $listener): void {
        $this->listeners[$event][] = $listener;
    }

    public function dispatch(EventInterface $event): void {
        foreach ($this->listeners[$event->getName()] ?? [] as $listener) {
            $listener($event);
        }
    }
}

// Rejestracja i wyzwolenie
$dispatcher->subscribe('user.registered',
    fn($e) => $mailer->sendWelcome($e->getPayload()['user_id']));
$dispatcher->subscribe('user.registered',
    fn($e) => $settings->createDefaults($e->getPayload()['user_id']));

$dispatcher->dispatch(new UserRegisteredEvent($user));
// Obaj listenery wywoływani automatycznie
```

